originalText.text:
After a lengthy online search for a real estate broker, I found Michele. Without meeting her I felt she was the right one to help me find the dream apartment. Happy to  say she did not disappoint! Michele is a gem! She is an experienced, trustworthy and knowledgeable professional with a wonderful, warm and easy going personality. She was there every step of the way, working with me at my own pace. I never felt pressured or rushed, and there never was a need to contact Michele twice to get answers to my questions. She makes time for you!
Michele is also well connected. She suggested an attorney and an insurance broker which I decided to go with, and I couldn’t have been happier with their services.
I highly recommend Michele, and I will not hesitate to contact her in the future if the need arises.
Looking forward to moving in and start enjoying my new home. Thanks Michele for all your help and for being you!

originalText.text: Michele Denby is such a pleasure to work with and was instrumental in helping us find the perfect condo for our family. From our first viewings to closing (and beyond!) - we've been so thankful to have worked with Michele. We have no idea where we'd be without her help and support through the process! She's extremely knowledgable, thorough, patient, responsive - the list goes on and on. She's exceeded our expectations with her continued support after our closing - helping us with contractor recommendations and checking in as we've been moving. Highly recommend working with her. Thanks, Michele!

originalText.text: Michelle was instrumental in making my move to NYC a pleasant and easy transition.  She first helped us secure our first ever apartment in NYC moving from the suburbs of Seattle.  We explored neighborhoods all over NYC and found our perfect neighborhood and first apartment.  Fast forward two years and Michelle helped us find the perfect condo for our family and we are so happy.  She was informative and honest, patient with us but diligent with prospects.  Michele knows this city like the back of her hand and we were so thankful to have her on our side through the process!

originalText.text: Michele found the perfect place for my roommates and I as we made our first move to NYC from Texas. Throughout the virtual touring process, Michele was great at communicating with us. She was responsive and available at all times when we needed her and was patient through every decision. She was very intentional and made sure to find us the perfect space that was safe, beautiful, and nearby everything that we would need as young adults. Would recommend her to anyone that is looking for an informative and trustworthy realtor! Thanks, Michele!
